    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, im a bit confused about some stuff happening at my kid's elementary school. they're starting to use these new lessons about gender identity in class. i've heard different things from other parents... some say it's good, others are pretty upset about it. can u help me understand what the different perspectives are around this?",
