    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the overview. i guess i'm wondering about the \"ideological\" part... some parents i've talked to seem to think the school is just trying to push a specific agenda and that the kids aren't even old enough to understand it. on the other side, people are saying that if we don't teach this stuff, we're basically leaving kids out in the cold. does it feel like one side has more of a solid ground to stand on, or is it just one big mess?",
