      "content": "that's a pretty strong way to put it. so you're saying the school is basically choosing an agenda over the kids' needs? what about the people saying this is just about being kind and making sure every kid feels safe and included? isn't that kind of a valid educational goal too, or is that also just part of the \"agenda\"?",
